      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ECHOES OF DAD (1) goes very well at this journey here having never missed the frame including four wins. Comes off a (34.33) win last time, scoring by a nose in a Other over 595m at this track. Looks well placed and should feature. MALLEE BEAUTY (6) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in her dazzling 30.14 win at this track over 530m. Rates a leading chance if runs up to recent winning time. BROTHER ERNEST (2) was game in defeat off the inside draw last start, finishing second and beaten 0.8 lengths (30.66) behind Cawbourne Adele at this track. Well-placed to take this out. NOLA KEEPING (3) profiles nicely here at this trip.",
